<div class="wrap">
  <div class="row text-center">
    <h1>yrsa</h1>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="landing-image">
        <%= image_tag 'yrsa2.png', class: "img-responsive img-rounded" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h2>
        <small>
          Have you ever wondered the stars of your favorite restaurant ratings are for? Is it for its service, food, or location? Which one is it? Wouldn't be nice if you can tell right away what makes that restaurant is 5 stars or 1 star? yrsa, which stands for your ratings snappy analysis, is about to change that.
        </small>
      </h2>
      <br>
      <hr>
      <br>
      <h3>
        <small>
          the premise is simple: break them down. User will have a choice whether to rate a place in general OR rate exactly of what they know.
        </small>
      </h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <br>
  <br>

  <% if !user_signed_in? %>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 text-center">
      <%= link_to "signup", new_account_path, class:"btn btn-lg btn-default" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    <div class="col-md-3 col-xs-6 text-center">
      <%= link_to "signin", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-default" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2"></div>
  </div>
  <% end %>

  <div id="push"></div>
</div>


<div id="footer">
  <div class="container">

  </div>
</div>
